sql:
SELECT club_name
FROM clubs
ORDER BY club_name;

external_knowledge:
- 'Total compensation' includes bonuses and incentives;
- 'Contracts signed' indicates that the negotiations have been completed and the contracts are finalized;
- The query focuses on clubs that have at least one player with a signed contract.

- The term "top-compensated" refers to the players with the highest total compensation within each club, up to the top 3;
- The total compensation includes bonuses and incentives;
- The query considers only players who earn more than $500,000 annually.

- "Stars who shine" refers to players with an average base salary greater than $100,000;
- "Grand arena of soccer" refers to the context of professional soccer;
- "Luminaries" refers to the players meeting the salary criteria.
